hour 1
hour 2
hour 3
hour 4
hour 5
hour 10
hour 15
hour 20

all of the above
StdLogic1164 '0':  display element off (brown or orange)
StdLogic1164 '1':  display element on  (red or yellow)
other values    :  display element undefined (cyan)

